title: MASSIVE EMPIRE SIEGE - Total War: WARHAMMER Mod Gameplay
description:
Total War: WARHAMMER Mod Gameplay - Starting today, I am on the hunt to find the perfect combination of mods to improve the Siege Experience for Warhammer.  In this massive siege battle between the Empire and Greenskins we are trying out the Radious Mod.  Enjoy the Battle :D

Mods:
Radious - http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=689913357&searchtext=

Units Mod - http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=693667798&searchtext=

Larger Units - http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=691918767&searchtext=radious 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
